<!DOCTYPE HTML>
<html>
<body>
    <div class="header-banner">
        <div class="wrap">
            <div class="banner">
                <div class="indent">
                    <h2 class="indent-left margin-bot" style="margin-left:250px">Meine Reisen durch die Welt!</h2>
                    <div class="banner-left">
                        <div class="con-text">
                            <div class="grid1-img">
                                <img src="~/web/images/glass.png" alt="">
                            </div>
                            <div class="grid1-desc">
                                <p>Restaurants</p>
                            </div>
                            <div class="clear"></div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="con-text">
                            <div class="grid1-img">
                                <img src="~/web/images/flight.png" alt="">
                            </div>
                            <div class="grid1-desc">
                                <p>Flüge</p>
                            </div>
                            <div class="clear"></div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="con-text">
                            <div class="grid1-img">
                                <img src="~/web/images/group.png" alt="">
                            </div>
                            <div class="grid1-desc">
                                <p>To Do Liste</p>
                            </div>
                            <div class="clear"></div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="con-text">
                            <div class="grid1-img">
                                <img src="~/web/images/key.png" alt="">
                            </div>
                            <div class="grid1-desc">
                                <p>Mietwagen</p>
                            </div>
                            <div class="clear"></div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="clear"></div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="header_bottom_right_images">

                        <div class="slider" style="width:660px;height:400px " >
                            <ul class="rslides" id="slider1">
                                @foreach (var x in Model)
                                { 
                                <li><img src="@x.BlogImage "style="width:660px; height:400px" alt=""></li>
                                }
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="clear"></div>
            </div>
            <div class="clear"></div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class"content">
        <div class="wrap">
            <div class="wrapper">
                <div class="con-top">
                    <h3>Herzlich Wilkommen zur unseren TravelBlog!</h3>
                    <p>In diesem Projekt nehme ich euch mit zu den ganzen Reisen die wir als Paar mit meiner Frau getätigt haben.Die gestaltung des Projekts wurde in C# MVC5 getätigt. Ich hoffe,
                       dass mei Projekt überzeugen kann und die Reise Orte ihnen gefallen. Viel Spaß beim durchforsten!
                    </p>
                </div>
              @Html.Action("Partial1","Home")
             
                <div class="grids">
                    <div class="box1">
                        @Html.Action("Partial3", "Home")
                        @Html.Action("Partial4", "Home")
                        <div class="clear"></div>

                    </div>
                  
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>

